      "title": "Colombo stock market gains on political developments",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo stock market gained sharply today in the aftermath of Saturday's peaceful revolt by the people against the incumbent regime.",
        "The active S&PSL20 Index gained by over 5% and the benchmark ASPI by over 3%. Turnover however was low at Rs. 811 million involving 53 million shares. Year to date the ASPI and S&PSL20 are down by over 40%."
      ],
